{"tid":2077561,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲軍師質素實在令人驚嘆","createTime":"2020-06-24T11:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T15:28:59.000Z","uid":500,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb16d91f6c4c9656bb42b4638d795b25b15a7abb","tid":2077561,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"唔關條片事 去睇留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zXP8XmSRdN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzXP8XmSRdN0&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0952d254\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zXP8XmSRdN0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭遇口舌戰空間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBB2qNd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBB2qNd.jpg&h=41ec977e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唇槍舌劍嘅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkPb3z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkPb3z4.jpg&h=d00d1838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n槍與劍嘅攻擊威力不平衡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqbxN3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqbxN3C.jpg&h=3d0dcfed&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n新友軍到達<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PP84EaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPP84EaK.jpg&h=b6d5b7e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n敵方重新展開口才攻勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYRBviy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYRBviy.jpg&h=0095774d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n結束我嘅回合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26P0cxL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26P0cxL.jpg&h=a3121e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先君子後小人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMx1GrB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMx1GrB.jpg&h=8a3ddf5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後仲有大量友軍 不過solom(a)n繼續以一人軍團之力嚟對抗佢嘅敵人<br />\n雖然佢喺文中冇講咁 但喺深讀佢嘅文章就可知佢已經齊晒藍絲癌嘅幾大症狀 我唔知 我睇唔到 我唔信等等...<br />\n以soloman嘅'一開始聽起上嚟幾有道理 但係聽聽下就知係死雞撐飯蓋'嘅辯論技巧仲可以維持到幾耐<br />\n本人自問爛唇一把 只能作出臭系之言 希望有心人可以會一會下佢 順便整理自己思緒 並且睇佢仲有啲咩新招可出"},{"pid":"039094976a037b1fcf309d503586ac8d0ceb178b","tid":2077561,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"你理佢咪on9囉<br />\n睇下咪算囉，仲走去留言<br />\n你唔係諗住留下言就可以屌醒班藍絲下嘛？<br />\n曬鳩氣啦<br />\n班人唔會醒架！大家一齊加速啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（冇睇過你d圖）"},{"pid":"77f60759b3403f489e8b7e4f8d192777be96eaaa","tid":2077561,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"有個資料庫收集咗藍絲常見言論同埋有關反駁<br />\n樓主你可以睇下，甚至幫手完善下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2048605\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2048605</a>"},{"pid":"ef07cab19a0e636b63431825dd6e6cdf08bfc85e","tid":2077561,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:54:32.000Z","msg":"其實對住d深藍係無乜野好講<br />\n基本上佢地基本論調就係你港獨，你分裂國家，你收美國錢"},{"pid":"fde2d560654a9304c21ca9d60e1fdb24b1a4c878","tid":2077561,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"wtf<br />\n條片勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弱智藍絲就由佢喇"},{"pid":"fd40ad30e9890fd7187f8c360694043e839a0fc4","tid":2077561,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"睇到臨尾喊左。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29309fb40ed6648eefd6c4c7ab9969c3411b7f90","tid":2077561,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77f60759b3403f489e8b7e4f8d192777be96eaaa","tid":2077561,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"有個資料庫收集咗藍絲常見言論同埋有關反駁<br />\n樓主你可以睇下，甚至幫手完善下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2048605\" target=\"_b